# Intuition
<!-- Describe your first thoughts on how to solve this problem. -->
It's a greedy algorithm.

# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
In each step pick the one calss that adding the extra student creates the bigger difference. I used a PriorityQueue to select the largest difference at each step. 

# Complexity
- Time complexity:
<!-- Add your time complexity here, e.g. $$O(n)$$ -->
$$O(n*log(n))$$
- Space complexity:
